Title: Payment by Card
Description: As a customer, I can make payment with card by entering card type, card number, card security code and expiry date, so that the system will verify the card and able to make payment.

Title: Update Customer Record
Description:
1. As a customer, I am allowed to update full name so that full name is corrected.
2. As a customer, I am allowed to update contact number so that contact number is corrected.
3. As a customer, I am allowed to update email address so that email address is corrected.

Title: View Customer Record
Description:
1. As a customer, I am allowed to view username so that I can verify the username is correct.
2. As a customer, I am allowed to view full name so that I can verify the username is correct.
4. As a customer, I am allowed to view contact number so that I can verify the contact number is correct.
5. As a customer, I am allowed to view email address  so that I can verify the email address is correct.
6. As a customer, I am allowed to view date of birth so that I can verify the date of birth is correct.

Title: Add Customer Record
Description:
1. As a customer, I am required to add username so that I can login
2. As a customer, I am required to add password so that I can login
3. As a customer, I am required to add full name so that I am recognize by driver and make reservation
4. As a customer, I am required to add contact number so that I can be contacted by driver and staff
5. As a customer, I am required to add email address so that i can receive the latest news and promotion
6. As a customer, I am required to add date of birth so that staff can send me birthday wishes and birthday promotion or voucher.

Title: View Reservation Record
Description:
As a customer, i can view my reservation record,so that i can verify my reservation information
As a customer, i can save my favorite location from reservation record.

Title: Update Reservation Record
Description: As a customer,I am able to update the pick up location and destination so that I do not need to make cancellation.

Title: Reservation Cancellation
Description: As a customer,i can cancel my reservation so that i will not waste my money.

Title: Add Reservation Record
Description:
As a customer,i can select pick up location and destination, so that i can make online reservation
As a customer,i can select pick up date and time, so that i can make online reservation

Title: Update Driver Record
Description: As a driver, i am allowed to update driver username, password, full name, ic number(unique), contact number(unique), email address(unique), home address, taxi company name, taxi plate number(unique), date of birth, license expiry date so that record is corrected.

Title: View Driver Record
Description: As a driver, i am allowed to view driver username, password, full name, ic number(unique), contact number(unique), email address(unique), home address, taxi company name, taxi plate number(unique), date of birth, license expiry so that can verify all detail is correct.

Title: Add Driver Record
Description: As a driver,I am required to add driver username, password, full name, ic number(unique), contact number(unique), email address(unique), home address, taxi company name, taxi plate number(unique), date of birth, license expiry date into database so that the database will register my detail as new driver.

Title: Customer Monthly Summary Report
Description: Allow staff to generate or view customer monthly summary report by selecting the desire month.

Title: Customer Yearly Summary Report
Description: Allow manager to generate or view customer yearly summary report by selecting the desire year.

Title: Reservation Exception Report
Description: Allow manager to generate or view reservation exception report by selecting the desire year and month.

Title: Reservation Monthly Summary Report
Description: Allow manager to generate or view reservation monthly summary report by selecting the desire month.

Title: Cancel Payment Record
Description: As a customer, I can delete the payment details according to the payment date so that the oldest payment records can be deleted.

Title: Driver Login
Description:
1. As a driver, I am required to enter username to login.
2. As a driver, I am required to enter password to login.

Title: Customer Password Recovery
Description:
1. As a customer, I am required to enter username and email address so that the system will send the new password through email.
2. As a customer, I am allowed to change password by entering new password so that I can login using new password.

Title: Driver Password Recovery
Description:
1. As a driver, I am required to enter username and email address so that the system will send the new password through email.
2. As a driver, I am allowed to change password by entering new password so that I can login using new password.

Title: Customer Login
Description:
1. As a customer, I am required to enter username so that I can login.
2. As a customer, I am required to enter password so that I can login.
